{"tid":600522,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"人美心善小天使！IU向聾啞人協會捐款5千萬！","createTime":"2018-03-21T11:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T13:57:07.000Z","uid":34643,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a015da930b21599c7fecd07a8b1f5aa7221c941d","tid":600522,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T11:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.asiachan.com/IU.full.41103.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.asiachan.com%2FIU.full.41103.jpg&h=3f6746cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌手IU為了聾啞老人們向聾啞協會捐出了5000萬元。<br />\n<br />\n在20日的時候，聾啞協會表示IU在16日捐出了5000萬元，關係者說「IU用本名李知恩捐出了款項，因為想要幫助有困難的人們，最後找上了聾啞老人援助中心。IU最近接觸了手語，因此對聾啞人士起了關心，同時是聾啞人士又是老人的狀況下似乎會更辛苦，因而選定了聾啞老人援助中心，非常感謝那份心意。」<br />\n<br />\nIU指定協會的聾啞老人援助中心進行捐款的契機是因為出演了tvN「我的大叔」的女主角的關係。<br />\n<br />\nIU在這部戲劇中飾演六歲開始就和生病的祖母單獨生活的20代女子李知安，劇中祖母的人物設定即為聾啞人士，IU學習了手語之後，理解了因為聽覺以及語言障礙而困難生活的老人們的心，因而做出了捐款的決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/g0gIoMsQNfs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fg0gIoMsQNfs&d=0rB%2F2xn9mIVBeqRBA0yYbYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=296bc45b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/g0gIoMsQNfs</a>"},{"pid":"eb1db6ba9f7d1edbb62d6e2b2b4ee72c24ada384","tid":600522,"uid":34643,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T11:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img2.ruliweb.com/mypi/gup/a/14/11/o/10785061951.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg2.ruliweb.com%2Fmypi%2Fgup%2Fa%2F14%2F11%2Fo%2F10785061951.jpg&h=9f11a2a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bfba1d97c7b1f7ac663f37f3b3a4f1fc9443a62","tid":600522,"uid":148541,"like":7,"dislike":45,"score":-38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ce35275c28d8383ad5ebacb70566c4968360316","tid":600522,"uid":113190,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"2bfba1d97c7b1f7ac663f37f3b3a4f1fc9443a62","tid":600522,"uid":148541,"like":7,"dislike":45,"score":-38,"citedBy":3